{"tid":1911584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商務及經濟發展局表示不會向TVB追收四億頻譜使用費","createTime":"2020-03-05T12:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T12:08:24.000Z","uid":22556,"like":16,"dislike":587,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"197cc9540a2fb2b942586d9d540a789b6978b591","tid":1911584,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局表示，免費電視持牌廣播機構須履行獨特的社會功能，政府不會徵收頻譜使用費，是否收取頻譜使用費，並非基於免費電視台按通訊局指示，播放某些特定節目。<br />\n<br />\n商經局表示，免費電視持牌廣播機構須為市民大眾，提供免費新聞、娛樂、教育和資訊，以及照顧不同類型和年齡層的節目，並播放政府宣傳短片，以及在緊急情況下，免費向公眾廣泛發放關乎重大公眾利益的信息。<br />\n<br />\n局方指出，過往因為香港電台沒有本身的電視頻道，要免費電視台播放港台節目，只是要求的其中一部分，目前已經沒有充分理據，繼續要求商營廣播機構播放港台節目。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #無綫電視 #免費電視<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3269316509843049/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3269316509843049%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaqyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=05f46502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3269316509843049/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"2d03b7da1845159e2f48969b856131990e03359b","tid":1911584,"uid":117679,"like":139,"dislike":4,"score":135,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"乜撚野「獨特社會功能」？講啲唔講啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c29d1a4d25b00355bd89cd871701ff9efb2bf60","tid":1911584,"uid":207247,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285ca4d62ca99e9d016c0348514485465388cc99","tid":1911584,"uid":21572,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"官商勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c2a18d14ece8a872a7f285812a213d9a69c29d","tid":1911584,"uid":282490,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"