\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abfb45f359a935af6d21b3618db43b937d97942","tid":1911584,"uid":267572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197cc9540a2fb2b942586d9d540a789b6978b591","tid":1911584,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局表示，免費電視持牌廣播機構須履行獨特的社會功能，政府不會徵收頻譜使用費，是否收取頻譜使用費，並非基於免費電視台按通訊局指示，播放某些特定節目。<br />\n<br />\n商經局表示，免費電視持牌廣播機構須為市民大眾，提供免費新聞、娛樂、教育和資訊，以及照顧不同類型和年齡層的節目，並播放政府宣傳短片，以及在緊急情況下，免費向公眾廣泛發放關乎重大公眾利益的信息。<br />\n<br />\n局方指出，過往因為香港電台沒有本身的電視頻道，要免費電視台播放港台節目，只是要求的其中一部分，目前已經沒有充分理據，繼續要求商營廣播機構播放港台節目。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #無綫電視 #免費電視<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3269316509843049/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3269316509843049%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaqyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=05f46502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3269316509843049/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"官商鄉黑又一例證"},{"pid":"b05a1a81271c5f70bcf88bd2efc7f3d982c476f7","tid":1911584,"uid":311057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"講個笑話 ICAC"},{"pid":"4a6989122731a1342b81c7ae023d63485b154478","tid":1911584,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"有錢唔拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4483bf3d6c70f3042d20d1e9dfd94c243b06026f","tid":1911584,"uid":302151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da4dba230a18fffc2180065a10ad7de7659169d5","tid":1911584,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"ICAC 呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.